$$
Var(\hat{\boldsymbol{\beta}}_{(p+1) \times 1})=  \left\{ \boldsymbol{X}_{n \times (ğ‘+1)}^{t} \boldsymbol{W}_{n \times n}^{(i)} \boldsymbol{X}_{n \times (ğ‘+1)}  \right\}^{-1}
$$

kemudian standard error dari $\hat{\boldsymbol{\beta}}_{(p+1) \times 1}$ adalah akar dari diagonal utama  $\left\{ \boldsymbol{X}_{n \times (ğ‘+1)}^{t} \boldsymbol{W}_{n \times n}^{(i)} \boldsymbol{X}_{n \times (ğ‘+1)}  \right\}^{-1}$.



